rong>Major media houses</strong> including NDTV, The Times of India and India Today order custom acrylic trophies for their award nights. The Big-4 <strong>consulting firms (Deloitte, EY, PwC, KPMG)</strong> in Gurgaon and the IT clusters in Noida are repeat clients for long-service and quarterly performance awards. Premier institutions such as <strong>IIT Delhi, Delhi University, JNU, AIIMS and FMS Delhi</strong> commission engraved mementos for convocations and prize-day ceremonies.</p><h3>Common occasions in Delhi NCR</h3><ul><li>Republic Day and Independence Day government awards</li><li>PSU long-service and retirement felicitations</li><li>Corporate annual conferences at ITC Maurya, Taj Palace and Hyatt</li><li>Convocation and academic excellence awards at IIT/DU/JNU</li><li>Media and advertising award nights</li><li>NGO and advocacy recognition events</li></ul><p>For bulk quotes, GST-compliant invoicing or rush delivery to NCR, WhatsApp <strong>+91 78922 07252</strong> or call <strong>+91 94801 50888</strong> — our team handles PO-based orders and ships pan-India daily.</p>",
